# Live Suggestions — Environment Variables
#
# This project has NO server-side secrets.
# The Groq API key is supplied by the user at runtime through the Settings UI
# and is stored in their browser's localStorage. It is never stored server-side.
#
# No .env file is needed to run or deploy this project.
# `vercel deploy` / `netlify deploy` / `railway up` work out of the box with zero config.
#
# If you ever add server-side secrets in the future, document them below:
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...   # Only if you want a server-side default key (not recommended)
